            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;@fuz actually, it&apos;s not even only the compiler that warns: the warning quoted in the OP was printed by the linker!&lt;/span&gt;

